Get free icons in Material Sharp design style

Our consistent Material Sharp icon pack follows the Material guidelines from Google, including the latest icon themes (filled, outlined, rounded, , and sharp versions for each icon).

  • All themes are pixel-perfect at 2424 pixels
  • These system icons cover a variety of common actions, files, devices, objects, and directories.

Material icon pack succeeds the previous icon pack for Android Ice Cream.

Download free Material Sharp icons in different themes for Android UI design. The graphics are available in both PNG and vector.
